window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>He is the one that never looks her way.</p> <p>He is handsome and strong.</p> <p>He is rough around the edges and mean.</p> <p>He is everything she’s ever wanted.</p> <p>He doesn’t even know she exists.</p> <p>Her life is a joke.</p> <p>She doesn’t step on cracks in the sidewalk.</p> <p>She laughs at inappropriate times.</p> <p>She talks when she shouldn’t.</p> <p>She is clumsy and trips on air.</p> <p>She is finally on his radar.</p> <p>God help her now.</p>"; 
